Speaker: SPEAKER_00
Text: About 55 different kinds of cockroaches are found in the United States.

Speaker: SPEAKER_00
Text: They carry filth on their legs and bodies and may spread disease by walking over food

Speaker: SPEAKER_00
Text: or leaving their bowel movements in food.

Speaker: SPEAKER_00
Text: They also leave behind a dark colored fluid,

Speaker: SPEAKER_00
Text: which they vomit from their mouths while feeding.

Speaker: SPEAKER_00
Text: Unless dishes are thoroughly washed before using,

Speaker: SPEAKER_00
Text: their bowel movements, mixed with this dark colored material,

Speaker: SPEAKER_00
Text: dark-colored material will give off a foul odor.
